    <body>
        <p>In the continuously changing world of technology, every organization strives to find the right balance between the highest levels of security, best user experience, and improved agility. Organizations want to enable frictionless access to resources while reducing the risk of security incidents, and adopt modern security frameworks while continually factoring in contextual and adaptive policies for accessing apps.</p>
        <p>Fundamental user behavior has also changed. It is now common for users to access critical organizational resources on their personal devices. Organizations face the challenge of enabling such access without the risk of data loss.</p>
